A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to state legislative districts; providing
2 legislative findings; requiring management council to assign
3 legislative apportionment to a committee of the legislature
4 for study during the 2025 legislative interim as provided by
5 this act; providing that legislation to apportion the
6 legislature based on the requirements of this act may be
7 introduced during the 2026 legislative budget session; and
8 providing for an effective date.
9
10 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
11
12 Section 1.
13
14 (a) The Legislature finds that:
